<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no" />
    <meta name="description" content="A list of all DEV.to posts by Tom Anderson (@ndsn)" />
    <meta name="author" content="Thomas Anderson" />
    <title>@ndsn on Dev.to</title>
  </head>

  <body>
    <h1>@ndsn on Dev.to</h1>
    <p>Below you will find links to all the posts that I have published on <a href="https://dev.to">dev.to</a>. This is a completely static site built with <a href="https://11ty.dev">11ty</a> that uses a JavaScript data file to call the Dev.to API at build-time and populate a collection.</p>
    <h2>Posts <small>(Pulled from <a href="{{ devtoapi.feed }}">Dev.to API</a>)</small></h2>
    <hr />
    <ul>
      {% for item in devtoapi.posts limit:5 %}
        <li>
          <h3><a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.title }}</a></h3>
          <p>{{ item.description }}</p>
          <p>Categories: {{ item.tag_list | join: ', ' }}</p>
          <p>Published on {{ item.published_timestamp | date: "%A %e %B %Y at %I:%M%P" }}</p>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
